                <h4>Indicators</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Moving Averages</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>35 SMA (Simple Moving Average)</li>
                            <li>6 EMA (Exponential Moving Average, open price)</li>
                            <li>5 EMA (Exponential Moving Average, close price)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Parabolic SAR (PSAR)</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Step: 0.018</li>
                            <li>Max: 0.08</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Commodity Channel Index (CCI)</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Apply to typical price (HLC/3)</li>
                            <li>Levels: +90 and -90</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <h4>Long Entry Criteria</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>6 EMA and 5 EMA must be above 35 SMA</li>
                    <li>PSAR should be below the price</li>
                    <li>MACD indicator should be above 0</li>
                    <li>CCI should be above +90</li>
                </ul>
                <h4>Risk Management</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Stop Loss: 35 pips</li>
                    <li>Trail Stop: 15 pips</li>
                    <li>Profit Target: 60 - 100 pips</li>
                </ul>
                <h4>Short Entry Criteria</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>6 EMA and 5 EMA must be below 35 SMA</li>
                    <li>PSAR should be above the price</li>
                    <li>MACD indicator should be below 0</li>
                    <li>CCI should be below -90</li>
                </ul>
                <h4>Risk Management</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Stop Loss: 25 - 45 pips</li>
                    <li>Trail Stop: 15 - 20 pips</li>
                    <li>Profit Target: 60 - 100 pips</li>
                </ul>
                <p>By following these guidelines, you can make informed trading decisions based on a combination of moving averages, PSAR, MACD, and CCI indicators. Always ensure to manage your risks with appropriate stop-loss and trail-stop levels to protect your capital.</p>
